      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TO PERU (1) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at Sandown over 595m behind Jorogumo (35.15) in a Grade 5. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from seven attempts. Can make amends. YOUNG RUFUS (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (24.37) at Traralgon behind Dr. Odin in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Can feature again. KENZIE KID (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (20.54) last time in a Grade 5 at Traralgon. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Better than last start and can bounce back. INVICTUS BLUE (4) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
